            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="24px" viewBox="0 -960 960 960" width="24px" fill="#FFFFFF"><path d="m517.85-480-184-184L376-706.15 602.15-480 376-253.85 333.85-296l184-184Z"/></svg>
